ass="wp-block-list"><!-- wp:list-item -->n<li>24 u00e0 faire</li>n<!-- /wp:list-item -->nn<!-- wp:list-item -->n<li>1 en cours</li>n<!-- /wp:list-item -->nn<!-- wp:list-item -->n<li>23 faites</li>n<!-- /wp:list-item --></ul>n<!-- /wp:list -->nn<!-- wp:paragraph -->n<p>6.8 (30)</p>n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->nn<!-- wp:list -->n<ul class="wp-block-list"><!-- wp:list-item -->n<li>17 u00e0 faire</li>n<!-- /wp:list-item -->nn<!-- wp:list-item -->n<li>1 en cours</li>n<!-- /wp:list-item -->nn<!-- wp:list-item -->n<li>12 faites</li>n<!-- /wp:list-item --></ul>n<!-- /wp:list -->nn<!-- wp:heading -->n<h2 class="wp-block-heading">Calendrier pour 2026</h2>n<!-- /wp:heading -->nn<!-- wp:paragraph {"backgroundColor":"light-green-cyan"} -->n<p class="has-light-green-cyan-background-color has-background">ud83dudccc On reste sur le jeudi mais on du00e9cale au 3<sup>e</sup> jeudi du mois.</p>n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->nn<!-- wp:separator -->n<hr class="wp-block-separator has-alpha-channel-opacity" //>n<!-- /wp:separator -->nn<!-- wp:paragraph -->n<p>La ru00e9union se termine u00e0 14 heures.</p>n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->nn<!-- wp:paragraph -->n<p><strong>La prochaine ru00e9union aura lieu le jeudi 15 janvier 2025.</strong></p>n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->nn#compte-rendu, #documentation","contentFiltered":"<p class="wp-block-paragraph">La 47<sup>e</sup> ru00e9union de lu2019u00e9quipe de la documentation de WordPress en franu00e7ais su2019est tenue le jeudi 5 du00e9cembre 2025 u00e0 13h heure franu00e7aise, en visioconfu00e9rence.</p>nnnn<figure class="wp-block-image size-large"><a href="https://fr.wordpress.org/team/files/2021/01/documentation-wordpress-team-fr_FR.png"><img width="1024" height="427" src="https://fr.wordpress.org/team/files/2021/01/documentation-wordpress-team-fr_FR-1024x427.png" alt="" class="wp-image-3246"/></a></figure>nnnn<h2 class="wp-block-heading">Ordre du jour</h2>nnnn<ul class="wp-block-list">n<li>Point avancement</li>nnnn<li>Mises u00e0 jour</li>nnnn<li>Calendrier 2026</li>n</ul>nnnn<h2 class="wp-block-heading">Personnes pru00e9sentes</h2>nnnn<ul class="wp-block-list">n<li>Bu00e9ryl de la Grandiu00e8re (<a href="https://profiles.wordpress.org/beryldlg/" class="mention"><span class="mentions-prefix">@</span>beryldlg</a>)</li>nnnn<li>Jenny Dupuy (<a href="https://profiles.wordpress.org/jdy68/" class="mention"><span class="mentions-prefix">@</span>jdy68</a>)</li>n</ul>nnnn<h2 class="wp-block-heading">Point avancement</h2>nnnn<p class="wp-block-paragraph">Depuis la derniu00e8re ru00e9union du 16 octobre 2025 :</p>nnnn<ul class="wp-block-list">n<li>aucun nouvel article traduitu00a0;</li>nnnn<li>7 articles u00e0 traduire ajoutu00e9su00a0;</li>nnnn<li>aucun article ru00e9digu00e9u00a0;</li>nnnn<li>2 nouveaux articles FR u00e0 ru00e9diger (Colonne latu00e9rale des ru00e9glages dans lu2019u00e9diteur de blocs et Transformation des blocs).</li>n</ul>nnnn<p class="wp-block-paragraph">Le pourcentage global du2019avancement est de 84%.</p>nnnn<h2 class="wp-block-heading">Mises u00e0 jour de la documentation</h2>nnnn<p class="wp-block-paragraph">Toutes les issues de la 6.7 et de la 6.8 ont u00e9tu00e9 reportu00e9es.</p>nnnn<h3 class="wp-block-heading">Point selon les versions</h3>nnnn<p class="wp-block-paragraph">6.4</p>nnnn<ul class="wp-block-list">n<li>3 u00e0 faire</li>n</ul>nnnn<p class="wp-block-paragraph">6.5</p>nnnn<ul class="wp-block-list">n<li>11 u00e0 faire</li>n</ul>nnnn<p class="wp-block-paragraph">6.6 (38)</p>nnnn<ul class="wp-block-list">n<li>23 u00e0 faire</li>nnnn<li>1 en cours</li>nnnn<li>8 faites</li>n</ul>nnnn<p class="wp-block-paragraph">6.7 (48)</p>nnnn<ul class="wp-block-list">n<li>24 u00e0 faire</li>nnnn<li>1 en cours</li>nnnn<li>23 faites</li>n</ul>nnnn<p class="wp-block-paragraph">6.8 (30)</p>nnnn<ul class="wp-block-list">n<li>17 u00e0 faire</li>nnnn<li>1 en cours</li>nnnn<li>12 faites</li>n</ul>nnnn<h2 class="wp-block-heading">Calendrier pour 2026</h2>nnnn<p class="has-light-green-cyan-background-color has-background wp-block-paragraph">ud83dudccc On reste sur le jeudi mais on du00e9cale au 3<sup>e</sup> jeudi du mois.</p>nnnn<hr class="wp-block-separator has-alpha-channel-opacity"/>nnnn<p class="wp-block-paragraph">La ru00e9union se termine u00e0 14 heures.</p>nnnn<p class="wp-block-paragraph"><strong>La prochaine ru00e9union aura lieu le jeudi 15 janvier 2025.</strong></p>n<p class="o2-appended-tags"><a href="https://fr.wordpress.org/team/tag/compte-rendu/" class="tag"><span class="tag-prefix">#</span>compte-rendu</a>, <a href="https://fr.wordpress.org/team/tag/documentation/" class="tag"><span class="tag-prefix">#</span>documentation</a></p>","permalink":"https://fr.wordpress.org/team/2026/01/15/compte-rendu-de-la-47e-reunion-de-lequipe-documentation-du-4-decembre-2025/","unixtime":1768468426,"unixtimeModified":1768468518,"entryHeaderMeta":"","linkPages":"","footerEntryMeta":"","tagsRaw":"compte-rendu, documentation","tagsArray":[{"label":"compte-rendu","count":111,"link":"https://fr.wordpress.org/team/tag/compte-rendu/"},{"label":"documentation","count":21,"link":"https://fr.wordpress.org/team/tag/documentation/"}],"loginRedirectURL":"https://login.wordpress.org/?redirect_to=https%3A%2F%2Ffr.wordpress.org%2Fteam%2F2026%2F01%2F15%2Fcompte-rendu-de-la-47e-reunion-de-lequipe-documentation-du-4-decembre-2025%2F&amp;locale=fr_FR","hasPrevPost":false,"prevPostTitle":"","prevPostURL":"","hasNextPost":false,"nextPostTitle":"","nextPostURL":"","commentsOpen":true,"is_xpost":false,"editURL":null,"postActions":"<nav class=\'o2-dropdown-actions o2-post-actions\'><button class=\'o2-dropdown-actions-disclosure genericon genericon-ellipsis\'><span>Actions de lu2019article</span></button><ul><li><a href="https://login.wordpress.org/?redirect_to=https%3A%2F%2Ffr.wordpress.org%2Fteam%2F2026%2F01%2F15%2Fcompte-rendu-de-la-47e-reunion-de-lequipe-documentation-du-4-decembre-2025%2F%23respond&#038;locale=fr_FR" title="Se connecter pour ru00e9pondre" class="genericon  genericon-reply" data-action="login-